---
layout: page
title: 图书
body_class: 'books-page'
permalink: '/books/'
---

<p>以下列出我翻译的 <%= site.data.books.size - 1 %> 本书，自己写的 1 本书，点击书名可查看详细信息。</p>
<ul>
  <% site.data.books.sort_by(&:date).reverse.each do |book| %>
  <li><span class="font-mono"><%= book.date.strftime "%Y-%m" %></span> 
    <% if book.url != '#' %>
      <a href="<%= book.url %>" title="<%= book.title %>" class="text-dracula-<%= book.color%> no-underline hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><%= book.title %></a>
    <% else %>
      <span class="text-dracula-<%= book.color%>"><%= book.title %></span><% end %><% if book.status %>【<%= book.status %> 】<% end %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
